<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">We just received your booking request - we are onto it!</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">You can find the details of your booking at the bottom of this email.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;"><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;"><strong>1. Wait for your booking confirmation SMS</strong></p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">We will assign your booking to the first available therapist, and send you a confirmation SMS when done.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;"><strong>2. Relax and enjoy your massage</strong></p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">Your therapist will arrive at your home or hotel 10 minutes before your appointment - and will have everything required for a perfect massage: professional massage table, essential oils, clean linen and towels, soothing music and the best hands in the business!</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;"><strong>3. Spread the love to get a Free Massage</strong></p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">Refer a friend to Blys, and you both get $10 off your next booking. That's 1 free massage for every 10 friend you refer!</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">Visit <a href="https://getblys.com.au/invite">https://getblys.com.au/invite</a> for details.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">A few things to note:</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">We will always try to assign your booking to your preferred therapist first. If your preferred therapist is not available, then your booking will be assigned to the first available therapist.
If we don't have any therapists available for the time & location of your booking, we will get in touch with you to organise an alternative time for your booking.</p>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">We look forward to seeing you :)</p>

